）在秋叶原以“<a href="https://www.aogirihighschool-akiba-valentine.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在秋叶原过情人节不开心吗？</a> ”为题在秋叶原开展各种活动。</p><p>除了青桐高中的奖品出现在秋叶原的游乐设施外，还将在“秋叶原UDX”、“秋叶原广播会馆”和“秋叶原小野电总店”的街景中发布限定视频。</p><p>另外，2月11日（周日），秋叶原某处将举办免费情人节巧克力发放活动。详细的分发地点和分发方式将在未来公布。</p><p>此外，还将举办青桐高中与堂吉诃德的合作活动。全国唐吉诃德店将开设快闪店。</p><p> （参考）<a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000000187.000089066.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">viviON新闻稿</a></p><h2>举办“Suo Patra x Sanrio Characters”临时专角</h2><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1431a04188a5d5b6dfd1dbb88f0f15b5-kix.aqyp0m1k201x-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1431a04188a5d5b6dfd1dbb88f0f15b5-kix.aqyp0m1k201x-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 339px) 100vw, 339px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1431a04188a5d5b6dfd1dbb88f0f15b5-kix.aqyp0m1k201x-jpg.webp 339w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1431a04188a5d5b6dfd1dbb88f0f15b5-kix.aqyp0m1k201x-212x300.webp 212w" width="339" height="480" /></a></p><p> 3 月 8 日起，三丽鸥动漫店池袋 P&#39;PARCO 店将与<a href="https://twitter.com/Patra_HNST" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Suo Patra</a>和三丽鸥角色合作举办快闪专区。</p><p>合作周边商品有使用合作插画的心形罐头徽章（共5种）、亚克力钥匙扣（共5种）、亚克力立柱（共1种）等。</p><p>此外，活动开始前，Sanrio Anime Store ONLINE 已开始预售商品。</p><p><a href="https://sanrio-animestore-a3.jp/title/225" target="_blank" rel="noopener">点击此处</a>了解销售地点。</p><p> （参考）<a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000000588.000012048.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">A3株式会社新闻稿</a></p><h2>加拿大VTuber经纪公司“Phase Connect”日本成员首次亮相</h2><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1431a04188a5d5b6dfd1dbb88f0f15b5-kix.ynwmmv1lhumb-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1431a04188a5d5b6dfd1dbb88f0f15b5-kix.ynwmmv1lhumb-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1431a04188a5d5